    <item>
      <title>勒庞领导的极右翼在法国大选前巩固领先地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/le-pen-s-national-rally-solidifies-lead-two-days-ahead-of-voting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国时间周日将举行提前立法选举的第一轮投票，在此之前，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼政党国民联盟巩固了领先优势，而埃马纽埃尔·马克龙领导的中间派政党和左翼政党联盟的追赶步伐则有所减缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/le-pen-s-national-rally-solidifies-lead-two-days-ahead-of-voting</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 07:39:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国通胀在选举前两天恢复放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/french-inflation-resumes-slowdown-two-days-before-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国通胀略有放缓 — — 这强化了欧洲央行开始削减历史高利率的决定，并为总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙在选举前两天带来了经济亮点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/french-inflation-resumes-slowdown-two-days-before-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 06:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员认为法国大选毫无胜算，数十亿美元损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/france-election-has-markets-on-edge-after-billions-of-euros-erased</link>
      <description><![CDATA[主权债务危机以来最严重的债券市场崩盘。企业急于在可能出现资金短缺之前锁定资金。股市遭受近 2000 亿美元的重创。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/france-election-has-markets-on-edge-after-billions-of-euros-erased</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德里机场顶棚倒塌致一人死亡；航班中断</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/delhi-airport-suspends-flights-after-heavy-rain-collapses-canopy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五凌晨，由于大雨，德里机场前院的一部分顶棚倒塌，造成一人死亡，因此德里机场暂停了 1 号航站楼的所有航班。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/delhi-airport-suspends-flights-after-heavy-rain-collapses-canopy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 03:08:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
